{"tid":611491,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返套以前睇過嘅電影","createTime":"2018-03-31T05:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T10:34:25.000Z","uid":167901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa3f99b4a2df001705e725b42fc152505cad4fb","tid":611491,"uid":167901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"係外國戲黎 講個老人家（男）有幾個仔女 大個之後各散東西  佢自己一個住但好掛住啲仔女同孫 好想有個gathering見下佢地 奈何個個都各有各忙 有一日個老人家嘅一個仔女唔知咩事失蹤定死咗 件事比其他兄弟姊妹知道咗 佢地就協議唔好比佢地老豆(個老人家)知道 跟住老豆發現異樣決定搭好遠車去佢地仔女住嘅地方搵佢地想知到底發生咩事 途中唔知心臟病定點跌咗啲藥跟住差啲出事 最後係happy ending大概係咁 <br />\n<br />\n想睇返次套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54ca4734815a9d00d820ef83740fcefe49dce6b","tid":611491,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"Everybody's Fine  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17683f0980f5da12ecfaa4a68e31020bebafea3b","tid":611491,"uid":167901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a54ca4734815a9d00d820ef83740fcefe49dce6b","tid":611491,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"Everybody's Fine  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"係啊嗚唔該你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}